      <p begin="00:36:29,802" end="00:36:33,216">Der var kun et hjerteslag.</p>
      <p begin="00:36:33,216" end="00:36:35,388">En af tvillingerne var d&#248;d.</p>
      <p begin="00:36:35,388" end="00:36:40,049"/>
      <p begin="00:36:41,558" end="00:36:44,390">Vi t&#230;nkte p&#229;, om det andet ogs&#229;<br/>ville stoppe med at sl&#229;?</p>
      <p begin="00:36:44,390" end="00:36:50,030"/>
      <p begin="00:36:50,030" end="00:36:53,147">Men l&#230;gen sagde, at det faktisk vil<br/>styrke den resterende</p>
      <p begin="00:36:53,157" end="00:36:56,525">babys chancer for at overleve.</p>
      <p begin="00:36:57,142" end="00:37:01,724">Jeg pr&#248;vede at minde mig selv om, at<br/>det ikke var meningen at det skulle v&#230;re.</p>
      <p begin="00:37:01,724" end="00:37:06,138">Jeg fors&#248;gte at fokusere p&#229; det nye<br/>liv og vores fem&#229;rige datter, Odessa</p>
      <p begin="00:37:06,138" end="00:37:08,715">og at sl&#229; oddsene.</p>
      <p begin="00:37:11,377" end="00:37:13,148">Ken og jeg kaldte endda<br/>vores datter for Odessa</p>
