      <p begin="00:38:14,184" end="00:38:17,316">og de mest ondskabsfulde<br/>af alle arterne.</p>
      <p begin="00:38:18,155" end="00:38:22,639">Hvordan benytter vi vores forbundethed til <br/>at besejre vores selvudslettende impulser?</p>
      <p begin="00:38:23,299" end="00:38:29,473">Handling og k&#230;dereaktioner</p>
      <p begin="00:38:29,853" end="00:38:33,504">- I 1914 var verden blevet s&#229; forbundet</p>
      <p begin="00:38:33,504" end="00:38:35,811">at en likvidering i Europa,</p>
      <p begin="00:38:35,811" end="00:38:42,034">startede en global krig der str&#230;kte sig<br/>til alle jordens kontinenter,</p>
      <p begin="00:38:42,034" end="00:38:45,251">og at et d&#248;dsfald ledte til <br/>femten millioner mere.</p>
      <p begin="00:38:45,251" end="00:38:47,290"/>
      <p begin="00:38:47,290" end="00:38:50,331">Krigen var s&#229; &#248;del&#230;ggende<br/>at da den endelig sluttede</p>
      <p begin="00:38:50,331" end="00:38:53,825">blev den deklareret for, <br/>krigen der ender alle krige.</p>
      <p begin="00:38:53,825" end="00:38:57,928"/>
      <p begin="00:38:57,928" end="00:39:02,168">Den uendelige fred varede femten &#229;r,</p>
