      <p begin="00:41:53,766" end="00:41:56,755">Hvis ikke, <br/>ville hendes blindtarm punktere.</p>
      <p begin="00:41:56,755" end="00:41:58,347">Men p&#229; hospitalet ville l&#230;gerne <br/>ikke operere</p>
